  abstract={Metaverse has attracted widespread attention all over the world since its inception, promising significant potential in shaping a better vision for human society. It is regarded as “the ultimate form of the Internet”. However, the metaverse is still in its infancy, and the research on the relevant system architecture, enabling technologies, and practical applications are far from mature. To foster the advancement of the metaverse, this paper proposes a general metaverse architecture from the aspects of the constituent elements, operating system, roles, interaction modes, security and regulation, and also discusses the key technologies in the metaverse. Finally, the potential industrial research perspectives and application scenarios of the metaverse are presented.},
